==English==
===Noun===
'''[[rate]] [[tart]]''' (''plural'' '''rate tarts''')
[[Category:English nouns]]

#(''informal'') A person who [[sign up|signs up]] for a [[credit card]] that has a special [[introductory]] offer, such as low or zero [[interest]] for a certain period, uses the card for the duration of the offer, then cancels the card and switches to another with a similar offer, and so on.

====Synonyms====
*[[card tart]]
*[[credit card tart]]